name: Treetop Legends: Alfredo's Epic Adventure (Part 1)
description:
In this new platform game, Alfredo dodges obstacles and fights enemies!

Treetop Legends is a series created by Nathan Pizano.

Music is from Hacienda Gardeners.

This game is brought to you by Warped Planet Studios.

There are no ads or in app purchases in this game.
